headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Double Rewards for Air Freight Cargo Sell Missions
content:
Slide into the cockpit to turn a huge profit this week: if your Hangar is overflowing, it’s time to offload. Luckily, all Air Freight Cargo Sell Missions are paying out double until March 10th, so there’s plenty of reason to move quickly and confidently.

As an added celebratory bonus, complete any Air Freight Cargo Sell Mission by the end of this week and return after March 15th to receive the Neon Glow Necklace and the Red and Blue Bangles.
